George Wyner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Wyner 0 George Wyner (born October 20, 1945) is an American film and television actor. Wyner graduated from Syracuse University in 1968 as a drama major, and was an in-demand character actor by the early 1970s. Wyner has made guest appearances in over 100 television series and co-starred in nine. He is known for his role as Assistant District Attorney Bernstein on the series Hill Street Blues and Colonel Sandurz in the film Spaceballs.
